    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>Pancake The Llama is a humble pig farmer who lives with his wife, The Mrs The Llama. One day The Llama's lives are turned upside down when The Mrs is stolen by a nasty corporate alpaca gang. Now, Pancake must go on a journey to rescue his wife from the evil clutches of the alpacas.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as Pancake The Llama on a quest to save The Mrs.<br></li><li>Kick, spit, and jump through 10 hand crafted levels.<br></li><li>An open level concept lets you take on each level in whatever order you choose.<br></li><li>Face off against a horde of alpacas, featuring 2 unique boss fights.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Development</h2>Alpaclypse was designed, developed, and released by a team of five students at Neumont College of Computer Science during a 10 week project course.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Team</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gus McGuire<br></li><li>Mark Nusser<br></li><li>Logan Bailey<br></li><li>Hailey White<br></li><li>Alan Buechner</li></ul>",
